@Goku even if the coinomi mnemonic is supported, the existing seed phrases will work
they are the same format used in the rest of the Komodo eco-system like Agama and other wallets

right now, you can use Agama or the Ocean qt wallet to convert your AtomicDEX seed phrase to privatekey (wif) that will be accepted by most of the other wallets

@AndrewVV you need to convert the atomicDEX seed words  to a wif using Agama <https://support.komodoplatform.com/support/solutions/articles/29000024495-export-private-key-wif-from-a-wallet-seed-or-pin-password>

the wif should be usable in all the other wallets

the way seed words are converted to addresses is different in the Komodo ecosystem compared to other wallets

